name: Spider-Man (Peter Parker)
description: A young man with spider-like abilities.

name: Captain America (Steven Rogers)
description: A super-soldier who fights for justice.

name: Wolverine (James "Logan" Howlett)
description: A mutant with regenerative healing and claws.

name: Iron Man (Anthony "Tony" Stark)
description: A billionaire inventor who fights in a powered suit.

name: Thor (Thor Odinson)
description: The Norse god of thunder and a member of the Avengers.

name: Benjamin Grimm (Earth-616)
description: A member of the Fantastic Four with rock-like skin.

name: Reed Richards (Earth-616)
description: A genius inventor and leader of the Fantastic Four.

name: Hulk (Robert Bruce Banner)
description: A scientist who transforms into a giant green rage monster.

name: Scott Summers (Earth-616)
description: A mutant with optic blast powers and a member of the X-Men.

name: Jonathan Storm (Earth-616)
description: A member of the Fantastic Four with the ability to fly and generate fire.
